OL,7,FCampaigners and MPs fighting to stop
OL,8,Fthe UK's poorest families from being
OL,9,Fforced onto energy prepayment this
OL,10,Fwinter say the Government must impose a
OL,11,Ffull ban after Grant Shapps told
OL,12,Fsuppliers to stop the practice.
OL,14,FThe Business and Energy Secretary
OL,15,Fannounced on Sunday he was writing to
OL,16,Fthe nation's gas and electricity firms,
OL,17,Ftelling them to end the "harmful and
OL,18,Fanxiety inducing practice" of forcibly
OL,19,Fmoving people on to the controversial
OL,20,Fmeters without taking "every step" to
OL,21,Fsupport them with their bills.
